    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 122</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 7th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> armor quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>A <em>stanching </em>suit of armor helps stop the flow of b lood from the wearer's wounds, automatically tightening like a tourniquet in the appropriate places while also magically reducing the severity of the wound. <em>Stanching </em>armor reduces hit point damage, ability damage, or ability drain by an amount equal to its enhancement bonus if the damage or drain was from a bleed effect. The wearer also adds the armor's enhancement bonus to Constitution checks to become stable.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>stabilize</em>, <em>cure critical wounds </em>or <em>lesser restoration</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus</p>",
